Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:04.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\a6}Wow, awesome! Poirot's really in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.85,0:00:06.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\a6}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:10.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\a6}A reporter came here a while back and said he was going to publish a piece about us,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:14.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}but I never expected that it'd be an article this big!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:16.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}You're even in there, Azusa-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:18.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}See, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:23.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}‘Taii-{\i1}kun{\i0}, a calico cat who frequents the café, and Azusa-{\i1}san{\i0}, a beautiful Poirot employee.’
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:26.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Right! She's even holding Tai-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:30.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Wow! Maybe calling me beautiful is a bit much...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.71,0:00:33.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Newspaper articles usually do exaggerate the facts, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.43,0:00:36.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}W-Well, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:39.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But there's nothing about you, Amuro-{\i1}niichan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:43.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh, I happened to be off work that day, because I wasn't feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.93,0:00:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}It's a pity that you missed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.40,0:00:48.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Especially since you're so handsome!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:54.36,Thoughts,,10,10,0,,{\be10}Well, one of the men in black wouldn't exactly want his face showing up in a random gourmet food magazine like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.24,0:00:58.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, right, wasn't there another kid in your group?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:01:00.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Ai-{\i1}chan{\i0} went home already.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.04,0:01:05.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}We did ask her if she wanted to come to Poirot to see Taii...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But apparently she suddenly remembered something she had to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:13.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}T-Talking about Taii!! Where is he?! Is he already here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.26,0:01:14.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Well, the truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.55,0:01:20.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Taii-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s been staying at my house since last week!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.14,0:01:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Are you sure that's the right thing to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:30.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Taii may be a stray cat, but he has a collar, so he must belong to someone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:37.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Still... He's turned up covered in scratches from getting into fights with other cats around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:39.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I couldn't help but worry about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:42.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}And there's a photo of him in that magazine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:48.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}If Taii's owner is really searching for him, I'm sure they'll see the article and turn up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:52.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}But it's not fair to keep Tai-{\i1}chan{\i0} all to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:57.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}And there's no way his owner would find such a tiny photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.55,0:02:00.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Maybe if it was on the Internet, but like this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:03.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}That's what you'd think, right? But we've got a surprise...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:04.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:08.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Is this the Café Poirot from the magazine?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.81,0:02:10.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Oh, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.60,0:02:17.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I read in that article... Apparently a cat turns up in the evenings to beg for food? There was a photo and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.99,0:02:18.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.16,0:02:22.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\a6}That's actually my cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:24.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\a6}I've been looking for him for the last six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:26.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:28.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}What're you trying to pull?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:32.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\a6}That's my family's cat, I know it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:34.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\a6}You shouldn't just say something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:39.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Wow! The owners really did turn up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:41.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}And not just one, but two!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:44.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}T-They're not the only two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:47.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}There's another one waiting inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:53.98,GreedNarr,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Let the refreshing autumn breeze blow away your summer fatigue!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:55.73,GreedNarr,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}A gallant and dashing deduction show!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:59.28,GreedNarr,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Three people claiming to be his owner?!\NTime for a Kogorō and Bourbon deduction tag-team!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:00.82,GreedNarr,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:02.28,GreedNarr,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:05.41,GreedNarr,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}His name? Detective Conan!
